original_title: Chris Jericho's Rock N' Wrestling Rager at Sea: Sea of Honor
overview: Streaming For Vengence!  The most unpredictable wrestling superstar is back with the most unpredictable show to date!  Chris Jericho brings you Chris Jericho's Rock and Wrestling Rager at Sea, your place to see the most interesting and colorful wrestlers on the scene today!  You want to see action? You'll have it! Chris Jericho, The Young Bucks, Kenny Omega, Cody, Marty Scurll, Dalton Castle, Christopher Daniels, Frankie Kazarian and many more - that's who you get with this intense experience!  Watch the incredible Sea of Honor tournament unfold! And for your main attraction - the true clash people want. Alpha Club vs. Bullet Club!
tagline: Combining the worlds of rock and wrestling with a once in a lifetime amazing vacation experience.
title: Chris Jericho's Rock N' Wrestling Rager at Sea: Sea of Honor
